Title: Grundfos Magna 3 D 50-120 F 280 circulating pump 1 x 230V PN6/10
Description: Ideal for creating high performance heating and cooling systems, the Grundfos MAGNA3 50 - 120 F single phase circulator pump is suitable for new installations and refits, offering excellent efficiency and built-in communication capabilities. With a canned rotor, this pump is a maintenance-free integral unit with no shaft seal and just two gaskets for sealing, while bearings are lubricated by the pumped liquid. Wirelessly connecting with the Grundfos GO Remote app, for advanced reporting and monitoring, MAGNA3 is suitable for mixing loops, heating and air conditioning surfaces, ground source heat pumps and small chillers and includes fieldbus communication via CIM modules as well analogue and digital inputs and configurable relays. Features include FLOWADAPT, reducing the requirement for throttling valves, and a built-in differential pressure and temperature sensor.
